@startuml
' Embedded standalone style block (replicated per file; standalone)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor White
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam nodesep 50
skinparam ranksep 60
skinparam padding 3
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

left to right direction

actor "Cliente (movil)\n[Administrador opcional]" as Cliente
boundary "CameraSearchScreen + ai.service\n(React Native)" as Boundary
control "similarity views/service\n(MS2 Django)" as Sim
control "embedding_service\n(encode_image)" as Embed
entity "ficct_product_embeddings\n(112-dim)" as Emb
database "AWS DynamoDB" as Dynamo

Cliente --> Boundary : 1: elige/toma foto (expo-image-picker)
Boundary --> Sim : 2: POST /ai/similarity/search/ (multipart, JWT)
Sim --> Embed : 3: encode_image()\n[pHash 64 + HSV 48 = 112-dim]
Embed --> Sim : 4: vector consulta
Sim --> Emb : 5: leer embeddings de catalogo
Emb --> Dynamo : 6: Scan ficct_product_embeddings
Dynamo --> Emb : 7: embeddings almacenados
Sim --> Sim : 8: similitud coseno y ranking
Sim --> Boundary : 9: matches + scores\n[alt: 0 matches / 401]
Boundary --> Cliente : 10: prendas similares / sin resultados
@enduml
